transcript.text: On print shop evolution started in 2008 to simplify technology for SME print companies now serving thousands of PSPS globally, including thirty plus amongst the top PI350.
We evolved our solution services communication with consistent upgrades year on year, having the latest technology trends and by working very closely with customers to drive their growth.
Initially we started with Do it Yourself flash based design tool for stationary and later added photo book products.
Now we have product specific configurable HTML53D studio to work on any device including packaging, canvas, photo, print and more.
Also we have integrated third party designer studios.
Initially we started storefront for only online sales as a print e-commerce.
Now we have mobile responsive bootstrap for e-commerce to provide consistent experience across multiple sales channels like online B2CB2B, resellers, walk in sales agent and more.
We started with a corporate storefront for SMEB 2B.

Now we have single solution to manage SMEB 2B large B2B franchisees and multinationals including Fortune 500 companies with auto profiling and multiple approval rules integrated with their Punch Out system.
Previously, our primary focus was offering online orders management.
Now we offer centralized print order management having a seamless post purchase experience for both online and offline orders.
We also helped one of our customers to reduce 6 employees to two using our job board artwork approval and production one.
Thousands of end to end third party integrations, tools for mailing service, designing tools, cloud storage, MIS accounting and many more are compatible.
Previously, products were imported and added through Excel sheets.
Now we have extensive product master options with formula based attribute price calculation, which also supports complex shipping pricing setup.
There was a separate solution for multi store trade printer as per business profile.

Now we have launched partnership management solution to serve franchisees, resellers and to help PSPS grow their partnership network with changing market needs without any change in management for customers and internal team.
Today, we are one of the most preferred IT partner for your web to print needs as flexible to integrate and synergize the best of technologies As for your need.
